                <listBibl><bibl>AE 1987, 0228.</bibl><bibl>M. Kajava, Arctos 20, 1986, 59-71. - AE 1987.</bibl><bibl>CIL 10, 06561.</bibl><bibl>ILS 0199.</bibl><bibl/></listBibl>
            </div>
